        <item>
            <title>【评测】Seraﬁm S3 云端游戏⼿掣　轻便舒适 + 支援多平台</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/serafilm-s3/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=serafilm-s3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/serafilm-s3/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:30:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Seraﬁm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Seraﬁm S3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222750</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>来自台湾的电竞配件品牌 Serafim 近日推出了 Serafim S3 云端游戏手掣，除了支援 USB-C Android 手机外，更可跨平台连接云端游戏打造，使用 <span class="Y2IQFc" lang="zh-TW">Xbox Game Pass、GeForce Now、Steam Link 等平台在云端畅游熟悉的游戏。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09297-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09297-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09297.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09312-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09312-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09312.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><h2>配件</h2><p>盒内有 Serafim S3 手机游戏手掣本体、 USB-C to USB-C 充电线（分别为 1 米及 3.3 米）、一份说明书和一对握把，无论玩家手大手细也合用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09300-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09300-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09300.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲随机附送的握把更加纤薄，适合手细的玩家</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09302-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09302-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09302.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左边为原生握把，右边则是随附的纤薄握把</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09307-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09307-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09307.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲徒手就能轻松替换握把</p><h2>实测 &#8211; Google Play 游戏</h2><p>这款游戏手柄使用 USB-C 就能连接手提电话，惟暂未支援 iPhone 15，所以小编就使用 Android 电话连接 Serafim S3。不过要留意，试玩前需要先下载「Serafim Console」应用程式。小编试玩了超音鼠和 Asphalt 8。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-6-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-6-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-6-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲需要先下载此应用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09321-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09321-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09321.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-5-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-5-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-1-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-1-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09323-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09323-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09323.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223695" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-2-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-2-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223697" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-4-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-4-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403071-4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由于 Serafim S3 使用 USB-C 连接，而非无线方式，因此按键基本上可以说是没有延迟，而且其蘑菇掣非常顺畅，没有飘移问题。Serafim S3 操作键位和平常游戏手掣一样，小编试用后觉得手感不俗，唯一要弹的就是手柄构造较单薄，略嫌手感轻飘飘的。</p><h2>实测 &#8211; PlayStation 5</h2><p>小编另外尝试使用电话连接 PS5 游玩 PS5 上的游戏。Serafim S3 官方表示不能使用 SONY 官方的应用程式，需要使用他们提供的「PSPlay:PS5 &amp; PS4 Remote Play」应用程式，而这个应用程式更索价港币 50.9 元。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-2-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-2-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-2-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲需要先下载这个应用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-1-248x580.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-1-248x580.jpg 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot_202403111-1-scaled.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲索价 50.9 元</p><p>其后就可连接 PS5 游玩。小编就试玩了《圣兽之王》 和《FF 7 REBIRTH》。小编怀疑是 Wi-Fi 稍慢，明显可见延迟颇为严重，玩 FF7 时延迟严重至影响正常游玩体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09325-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09325-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09325.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《圣兽之王》</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09340-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09340-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09340.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲《FFVII Rebirth》</p><h2>总结</h2><p>如果平时喜欢使用手机装置玩云端游戏的玩家，可以尝试用 Serafim S3 手掣入门。小编试玩过这款手掣后，觉得手感颇舒适，而且手掣蘑菇掣没有飘移问题，非常顺畅。唯一要弹的是，小编是 PS5 玩家，而这款手掣的布局是 XBOX 式 ABXY，需要些时间适应。除此之外，小编觉得这款手掣造工较为单薄，比较脆弱，而且如果要使用 PS5 Remote Play 的话，仅能够使用非官方应用程式，该第三方应用程式除了索价 50.9 元外，更有资安隐患。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1223731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09335-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09335-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09335.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/serafilm-s3/review-2/">【评测】Seraﬁm S3 云端游戏⼿掣　轻便舒适 + 支援多平台</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
