        <item>
            <title>PS5 Pro 规格泄漏文件或属实，外媒：SONY 已展开内部调查</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/sony-investiagte-ps5-pro/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-investiagte-ps5-pro</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/sony-investiagte-ps5-pro/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 08:05:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225409</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日稍早前，我们报道过外媒爆料有关 PlayStation 5 Pro 的规格（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/">相关报道</a>），据报这批资料准确度甚高。以往官方一般不会对这类爆料作任何回应，但是次 SONY 罕有地就爆料文件展开内部调查，侧面反映出这次的消息可信度极高，今年很有机会出现 PS5 Pro 新机。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">As expected, Sony has launched an internal investigation into the leaked documents on Trinity as it leaked during a third-party rollout. </p><p>Not sure on the implications yet as I don&#39;t think they can catch one individual, but Sony could reduce its third-party developer pool for new…</p><p>&mdash; Tom Henderson (@_Tom_Henderson_) <a href="https://twitter.com/_Tom_Henderson_/status/1769811233237065881?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 18, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>外媒《InsiderGaming》早前报道过 PS5 Pro 的规格，创办人 Tom Henderson （X 帐户：<a href="https://twitter.com/_Tom_Henderson_">@_Tom_Henderson_</a>）昨日（19 日）在 X （前称 Twitter）发文表示 Sony 已经就 PS5 Pro 规格泄漏展开内部调查，现阶段尚未确认影响，而且据 Tom Henderson 估计 Sony 未有捉到泄密者，但估计 Sony 将会减少第三方开发者加入研发工作。</p><p>有兴趣深入了解 Sony PlayStation 5 Pro 规格的朋友可以看看我们先前的报道。连结：<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/">https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/_Tom_Henderson_/status/1769811233237065881">Tom Henderson@X</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/ps5-pro-rumors/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Pro 规格外泄　外媒：光线追踪性能强 3 倍 + 支援 8K</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/17/ps5-pro-specs-2024/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Pro 传年底推出　效能快 45% 支援更稳定输出</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/14/ps5-16/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5「重大」系统更新　PS5 机身显示灯更光 + 手掣声量增大</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/20/sony-investiagte-ps5-pro/fun-tech/">PS5 Pro 规格泄漏文件或属实，外媒：SONY 已展开内部调查</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
